# Tags
## TopLevel
snippet WindowSurround
alias   Window
abbr    <Window></Window>
    <Window x:Class="${1:#:ClassPath}" xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml" Title="${2:Window}" Width="${3:525}" Height="${4:350}">
        ${0:TARGET}
    </Window>

## Panel Types
snippet WrapPanelSurround
alias   WrapPanel
abbr    <WrapPanel></WrapPanel>
    <WrapPanel>
        ${0:TARGET}
    </WrapPanel>

snippet StackPanelSurround
alias   StackPanel
abbr    <StackPanel></StackPanel>
    <StackPanel>
        ${0:TARGET}
    </StackPanel>

snippet GridSurround
alias   Grid
abbr    <Grid></Grid>
    <Grid>
        ${0:TARGET}
    </Grid>

## DataGrid
snippet DataGrid
abbr    <DataGrid x:Name=""/>
    <DataGrid x:Name="${1:#:Name}"${0:TARGET}/>

snippet DataGridSuround
abbr    <DataGrid x:Name=""></DataGrid>
    <DataGrid x:Name="${1:#:Name}">
        ${0:TARGET}
    </DataGrid>

snippet DataGridColumns
abbr <DataGrid.Columns></DataGrid.Columns>
    <DataGrid.Columns>
        ${0:TARGET}
    </DataGrid.Columns>

snippet DataGridTextColumn
abbr <DataGridTextColumn/>
    <DataGridTextColumn${0:TARGET}/>

